  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA91">
<l>piṉṉā larunarakañ cērāmaṟ pētuṟuvīr</l>
<l>muṉṉāl vaṇaṅka muyalmiṉō – paṉṉū</l>
<l>laḷantāṉik kārkkaṭalcūḻ ñālattai yellā</l>
<l>maḷantā ṉavaṉcē vaṭi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So as not to join hell which is difficult [to bear] later on, you who are foolish,</l>
<l>early on make an effort to bow before the red feet of him</l>
<l>who measured all these worlds surrounded by the rain[-filled] ocean,</l>
<l>before him who took the measure of many treatises.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
